#: ../../C/creeping-featuritis.rst:5
msgid "creeping featuritis"
msgstr "creeping featuritis"

#: ../../C/creeping-featuritis.rst:7
msgid "/kree´ping fee'·chr·i:\\`t\\@s/, n\\."
msgstr "/kree´ping fee'·chr·i:\\`t\\@s/, 名詞"

#: ../../C/creeping-featuritis.rst:9
msgid ""
"Variant of :ref:`creeping-featurism`\\, with its own spoonerization: feeping"
" creaturitis. Some people like to reserve this form for the disease as it "
"actually manifests in software or hardware, as opposed to the lurking "
"general tendency in designers' minds. (After all, -ism means ‘condition’ or "
"‘pursuit of’, whereas -itis usually means ‘inflammation of’.)"
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`creeping-featurism`\\ の変種で、独自のスプーナリズムを持ちます。すなわちfeeping "
"creaturitisです。設計者の心に潜む一般的な傾向に対して、ソフトウェアやハードウェアで実際に現れる病気のために、この形を取っておくのを好む人もいます。(なにしろ、-ismは‘状態’や‘追求’を意味し、-itisは通常‘炎症’を意味するのですから。)"
